<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svasti śrī</hi> {<hi rend="grantha">meykkīrtti</hi>} {end of the line missing}
<lb n="2"/>kuṉṟakkūṟṟattu maṉṉupperumpaḻuvūrt tiru <g type="kaḻañcu"/> <unclear>t</unclear>toṟṟamuṭaiya<hi rend="grantha">mahāde</hi>vaṟku vāṇakovaraiyaṉ cuttamallaṉ <unclear>U</unclear> <g type="kaḻañcu"/> tta[<unclear>maco</unclear>] <g type="kaḻañcu"/> ḻaṉāṉ Ilaṅke<hi rend="grantha">śva</hi>ra<unclear>n</unclear>eṉ I<unclear>ttevaṟ</unclear>kku tirucceṉṉa[<unclear>ṭai</unclear>]<unclear>p</unclear> puṟamāka pūmi ceytu kuṭutta paric[<unclear>ā</unclear>] <g type="kaḻañcu"/> <unclear>vatu Ippa</unclear> <g type="kaḻañcu"/> ḻuvūr naka[<unclear>ra</unclear>]ttār iṭai [<unclear>nā</unclear>]<unclear>ṉ</unclear> mukkaḻai<unclear>ñ</unclear> {end of the line missing}
<lb n="3"/>[<unclear>llai</unclear>] ma<hi rend="grantha">hā</hi>tevi viṇṇakar āḻvār nilattukku vaṭak <g type="kaḻañcu"/> kum vaṭapāṟkellai Iraṇamukarāmaṉ vāykkālukku teṟkum kiḻakku cuttamali va <g type="kaḻañcu"/> <unclear>ti</unclear>kku me <g type="kaḻañcu"/> ṟkum Āka nāṉkellaikkum Uṭpaṭṭa nilam Orumā Iṉṉilam Orumāvum tirutti Itevaṟkku <g type="kaḻañcu"/> <unclear>tiruppa</unclear> <g type="kaḻañcu"/> ṭimāṟṟukku <unclear>t</unclear>evatānamāka ca {end of the line missing}
</p>

